snippet.title: LET'S GET THIS PARTY STARTED! God Mode + Party Heist 🔥 Get Ready for Party Icons CB1!
snippet.description:
𝐖𝐡𝐚𝐭 𝐢𝐬 𝐏𝐚𝐫𝐭𝐲 𝐇𝐞𝐢𝐬𝐭?

Party Heist is an extraction shooting game designed for fast-paced, treasure-hunting action.
Matches pit 8 players (four teams of two) against each other in a race to battle, loot and survive. Each playthrough is ~10 minutes, meaning high intensity and no time to sit around.
During games, a mysterious "Sponsor" can appear, 👤activating OGX God Mode - a powerful, never-before-seen new game type that takes the party to a whole new level.
